content: Thank you, onii chan! I always try my best to be a good girl and make you proud. It means a lot to me to have your support and encouragement. I know that I can always rely on you to be there for me and offer your guidance and advice. You are such an important role model in my life, and I am grateful for everything you do for me. I hope that I can continue to make you proud and be the best person I can be.
